Example usage:
perl pingsrvs.pl -s mail.isp.net -f pinghosts.conf "Alertee <bob@alertme.com>, Janice <janice@imawench.xxx>"

Pinghost configuration:
host.or.ip protocol(service, port, service, ...)
next.host ...

Services are as defined in /etc/services

